node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Nabela Noor Home on August 04, 2021 tagging @nabela, and @saaraandbegum. May be an image of 1 person, standing and indoor.

node.text:
It’s official! @saaraandbegum is HERE!! 🌿✨⁣
⁣
I am so honored to introduce to you my home brand named in honor of my grandmothers, Saara Syed and Begum Ayesha Noor. ⁣
⁣
The last year of my life has been so transformative and fulfilling thanks to my #pocketsofpeace series, which unleashed my biggest journey of self-discovery and allowed me to uncover my passion for homemaking.⁣
⁣
I want to be a part of your journey in practicing self-love through self-care, and I want to help provide meaningful touches to your home as you make time for you, because you deserve it.⁣
⁣
Saara & Begum is a true celebration of small town Pennsylvania living and South Asian heritage - and is rooted in family values, love and togetherness. ⁣
⁣
I am so thankful to launch this brand with my husband @itssethmar, and that he had the opportunity to meet my maternal grandmother, Saara in Bangladesh before she passed this year. ⁣
⁣
I hope both Saara & Begum are blessing this adventure from heaven, and that we can capture their essence through every collection. ⁣
⁣
Love you Nanu and Dadi. 💕⁣
⁣
Our Flagship Launch is available for purchase NOW on our website saaraandbegum.com 💫⁣
⁣
Be sure to follow @saaraandbegum to stay updated on all future launches and home inspiration!

node.text:
celebrating my thirtieth couldn’t have been more magical. ⁣
⁣
it wouldn’t have been possible without some of the most loving and talented humans and businesses: ⁣
⁣
🤍 planned by: @neharikanoor & @sadiaali.xo 
🤍 decorations by: @atozdecors 
🤍 florals by: @floralsbyyamileth 
🤍 chai cart by: @lachaicart 
🤍 biscuits from: @biskoot.co 
🤍 cake by: @farmhouse_cakes 
⁣
thankful for another year. ⁣
excited for the priceless adventures ahead. #pocketsofpeace #nabelanoorhome
